oh, King George County, Virginia|Shiloh]]\n* [[Weedonville, Virginia|Weedonville]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Notable residents==\n* [[James Madison]], fourth President of the United States\n* [[Mark Warner]], US Senator, maintains a residence and farm\n* [[Krystal Ball]], political talk show co-host and one-time Congressional candidate, grew up in King George\n* [[Collette Wolfe]], actress, grew up in King George, Virginia<ref>{{cite web|title=Colette Wolfe|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2180792/|publisher=IMDB}}</ref>\n* [[Jermon Bushrod]], guard for the New Orleans Saints in the National Football League (NFL), grew up in King George, Virginia<ref>[[Jermon Bushrod]]</ref>\n* [[Al Bumbry]], Major League Baseball Player\n* [[Nell Zink]], American novelist, grew up in King George County<ref>{{cite journal |last=Schulz |first=Kathryn |date=May 18, 2015 |title=Outside In |url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/05/18/outside-in |journal=New Yorker}}</ref>\n* [[Dorthia Cottrell]], Musician, grew up in King George County\n\n==See also==\n* [[Caledon State Park]]\n* [[National Register of Historic Places listings in King George County, Virginia]]\n* [[Northern Neck George Washington Birthplace AVA]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|King George County, Virginia}}\n* [https://www.kinggeorgecountyva.gov King George County Administration]\n* [http://www.kgcs.k12.va.us/ King George County Public Schools]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20181030035435/http://www.kghistory.org/ King George County Historical Society]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120306181817/http://resources.rootsweb.ancestry.com/USA/VA/KingGeorge/ RootsWeb King George County]\n* [http://www.onlinegis.net/VaKingGeorge/ King George County Online GIS]\n\n{{Geographic location\n|Centre    = King George County, Virginia\n|North     = [[Charles County, Maryland]]\n|Northeast =\n|East      = [[Westmoreland County, Virginia|Westmoreland County]]\n|Southeast = [[Essex Coun